al.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.331948, "shard": "06", "shelf_id": "sn84031081, 1921-03-14, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/nmu", "subject": ["albuquerque", "bernalillo county (n.m.)", "albuquerque (n.m.)", "bernalillo", "bernalillo county", "newspapers", "new mexico", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Albuquerque (N.M.)--Newspapers", "Bernalillo County (N.M.)--Newspapers", "New Mexico--Albuquerque", "New Mexico--Bernalillo County", "United States--New Mexico--Bernalillo--Albuquerque"], "subjects": [{"albuquerque": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:albuquerque&fo=json"}, {"albuquerque (n.m.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:albuquerque+%28n.m.%29&fo=json"}, {"bernalillo": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:bernalillo&fo=json"}, {"bernalillo county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:bernalillo+county&fo=json"}, {"bernalillo county (n.m.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:bernalillo+county+%28n.m.%29&fo=json"}, {"new mexico": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:new+mexico&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2022-11-22T21:13:11.488Z", "title": "Albuquerque morning journal (Albuquerque, N.M.), March 14, 1921, (CITY EDITION)", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84031081/1921-03-14/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://lccn.loc.gov/sn84031081", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84031081/", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/89574b58-4f2f-5ef6-b2bc-2b60260f4e52"], "batch": ["nmu_christie_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1903", "description": ["Daily Whole no. 9706 (Oct. 7, 1903)-v. 189, no. 80 (June 19, 1926). Carries designation of Morning journal and Morning Democrat, Oct. 7, 1903- Numeric designation includes several changes in the numbering syste